  p Victims' Information Service (VIS) connects you with the local victims' support provided through your Police and Crime Commissioner.
  p It also provides:
  ul
    li the information you need to understand the justice process
    li everything you are entitled to or can expect if you are a victim of crime
    li information on how to make a complaint or get compensation
